title: In Pixel 2 Device Flashed by taimen image from Flashtool.How to revert it actual android OS 10?
content:
Hi,
  In my pixel2 device OS version 10, i have flashed  Developer preview 11 version 4 by using Android Flash Tool. But instead of Walleye flash image wrongly updated with taimen flash image.
How can i revert from taimen to walleye or how can i revert to previous OS build. Please give me solution.

Thanks,
Dhinakaran T
